*& Subject: 1일부터 해당월의 마지막날까지는 셀력션 옵션스의 초기값으로 출력해봐라.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*

REPORT  Z_TH0701_MONTHDATE.
data last_date TYPE sy-datum.


************************************************************************
* 셀력션 옵션스
************************************************************************
SELECT-OPTIONS :
date for sy-datum.

************************************************************************
* 초기값 설정
************************************************************************
INITIALIZATION.

************************************************************************
* 초기값 설정 1. 해당월의 마지막 날짜를 구한다. 'LAST_DAY_OF_MONTHS'.
************************************************************************
CALL FUNCTION 'LAST_DAY_OF_MONTHS'
EXPORTING
  DAY_IN = sy-datum
  IMPORTING
    LAST_DAY_OF_MONTH = last_date.

************************************************************************
* 초기값 설정 2. 1일을 만들고, 초기값을 입력해준다.
************************************************************************
  date-sign = 'I'.
  date-option = 'BT'.
  date-low = sy-datum.
  date-high = last_date.
  date-low+6(2) = '01'.
APPEND date.

